<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="E客戶">
  <data key="d0">E客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">E客戶 is an entity representing a client or customer organization for which detailed maintenance records are systematically maintained. These organizations include E 고객, emphasizing the need to keep comprehensive documentation pertaining to their interactions and services received. The maintenance records can cover various forms of service provision, such as maintenance work conducted, ongoing support provided, and historical maintenance services rendered.

Specifically, E客戶 has Splunk maintenance records, highlighting a particular focus on Splunk-related activities within their maintenance history. Additionally, the maintenance record for E 고객 includes specific work items related to Forcepoint Endpoint DLP Data Containment and Checkpoint LogCLM UF Log Limit Adjustments, indicating that these services are part of the broader maintenance support provided.

In summary, E客戶 denotes a client organization for which comprehensive maintenance documentation is consistently managed. This documentation encompasses all aspects of their relationship involving maintenance services, including but not limited to those related to Splunk and other specific technical solutions like Forcepoint Endpoint DLP and Checkpoint LogCLM UF Log Limit Adjustments.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is an organization whose maintenance record includes work conducted by C人员.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a customer that underwent maintenance for Splunk in November 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client that received maintenance for Splunk in October 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client for whom maintenance records are kept.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-738a58105cbf665748b3257e0cfee9ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96</data>
