  <data key="d3">chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-490df5a6810de4f040c4fe2681e6ed6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0773b8daffa7a65254a73867e36afb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-738a58105cbf665748b3257e0cfee9ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcf7e8f6051fb59b7f2cec85fa4dc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-203eba714089c79438cfc39755f054ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56b76e765b58a558604d5d6f2575d2ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a81645d1d338ac013fa594b14c35640&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd</data>
  <data key="d2">World Athletics Federation is an organization that plays a pivotal role in overseeing global athletics events, including the World Athletics Championships. Its responsibilities encompass managing and validating athletic records to ensure their accuracy and integrity on a worldwide scale. The federation also governs the rules and standards for various athletic competitions and records, ensuring consistency and fairness across different events and regions. Additionally, it is responsible for the administration of major championships and the verification of athletes' performance records, contributing significantly to the governance and credibility of global athletics. The World Athletics Federation oversees global athletics competitions and record validations, playing a crucial role in maintaining the integrity and standards of athletic achievements worldwide.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
