  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">B人員, also referred to as B人员, is an engineer responsible for handling various aspects of maintenance work. This includes managing maintenance records and overseeing the maintenance process. The descriptions consistently highlight B人員's role in ensuring that maintenance-related duties are carried out efficiently and accurately, particularly in relation to C客戶. Additionally, there is mention of B人員 being involved with D客户的 maintenance process, indicating a broader scope of responsibility across different clients.

B人员作为工程师，负责处理维护工作。具体而言，B人員在C客户的维护过程中扮演重要角色，包括管理维护记录和监督整个维护过程。除了C客户之外，B人員还涉及D客户的维护流程，表明其职责范围涵盖了多个不同的客户群体。

In summary, B人員 is an engineer with a critical role in managing and overseeing maintenance activities for multiple clients. Their responsibilities include ensuring the efficiency and accuracy of maintenance-related tasks, particularly as they relate to both C客戶 and D客户.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance activities.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer handling the maintenance work for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling maintenance tasks for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is another engineer involved in handling the maintenance task.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the handling engineer responsible for conducting maintenance activities.</data>
