<node id="A人員">
  <data key="d0">A人員</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">A人员 is an engineer with a critical role in overseeing system and facility maintenance activities across multiple clients. Their responsibilities include managing maintenance records and conducting specific maintenance work to ensure operational readiness and system integrity. A人员 collaborates within the engineering team to ensure comprehensive coverage of all maintenance needs for various clients, including B客户, F客户, G客户, I客户的维护记录 (I customer's maintenance record), and A客户’s system.

On December 24, 2025, A人员 was specifically tasked with the maintenance of B客户的设施 (B customer’s facility). This highlights their involvement in on-site maintenance activities as well as record-keeping duties. Beyond this specific assignment, A人员 is also involved in maintaining records and conducting necessary maintenance work related to F客户 and G客户.

A人员's responsibilities encompass both administrative tasks such as handling maintenance records and performing essential on-site maintenance activities required for operational readiness and system integrity. They are the engineer who handled the maintenance record for B客户 and performed the maintenance process for I客户, further emphasizing their role in maintaining detailed documentation and ensuring that all necessary work is completed efficiently.

In summary, A人员 is an integral part of the engineering team responsible for effective and efficient maintenance activities across various clients. This includes a dedicated focus on both administrative tasks related to record-keeping and hands-on on-site maintenance tasks, particularly with respect to B客户’s system, F客户's system, G客户's facility, I客户的维护记录 (I customer's maintenance record), and A客户’s system.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is an engineer who conducted maintenance activities for B客戶on 2025/12/24 from 13:30 to 20:00.&lt;SEP&gt;A personnel is an engineer involved in the maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is one of the handling engineers responsible for the maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance record of I客戶.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-490df5a6810de4f040c4fe2681e6ed6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5618eb566fb322ada0eb69bef88a7581&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-726c374f489423e007bce76f7810b46e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67cc5a5ed7a1cbea5f9e6d5f5d08ab51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcf7e8f6051fb59b7f2cec85fa4dc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-203eba714089c79438cfc39755f054ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-56b76e765b58a558604d5d6f2575d2ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-886b4b629f3088ef8656c792cf7b3e8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7743e93210e95e8e40e0d2a627684b7</data>
