<edge source="E客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">17.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人員, E客戶) is a relationship where C人員 provides comprehensive maintenance and support services to E客戶. This role involves conducting various maintenance activities and handling tasks as needed, ensuring that all maintenance activities are carried out efficiently and effectively to maintain E客户的 operational integrity. The scope of responsibilities includes both regular upkeep and support of E客户的 assets during specified time periods.

C人員 performs these maintenance services at designated times as documented in records such as Splunk. This encompasses a wide range of tasks designed to address any issues or needs that arise promptly, ensuring the smooth operation of E客戶's systems and facilities. Specific work items are handled according to the documentation provided in their work record, reflecting a structured approach to service delivery.

C人員’s duties extend beyond routine maintenance; they also provide ongoing support services to E客戶, addressing issues and fulfilling requests efficiently as documented. This relationship emphasizes C人员's commitment to maintaining E客户的 operational effectiveness through timely and thorough maintenance and support activities.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員performed maintenance services for E客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provides maintenance services to E客戶.</data>
