<edge source="C人員" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B客戶, C人員) describes a relationship where C人員 provides maintenance services to B客戶. This includes documenting any issues and actions taken during the service period. Maintenance activities are carried out by both A人员 and C人员 for B客户. Specifically, C人员 is responsible for providing maintenance services that may involve addressing specific technical problems, such as those related to an IDX hard drive issue.

C人員 not only conducts regular maintenance tasks but also offers engineering support to B客户提供维护服务和技术支持. This role encompasses a wide range of responsibilities including handling various maintenance issues and ensuring the smooth operation of B客户的 systems and equipment through consistent service provision.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員assists in maintaining B客戶's systems and collaborates with other engineers.&lt;SEP&gt;C人员provided maintenance services for B客户.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員also provided maintenance services to B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人员provided maintenance support for B客戶during a specific period in December 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is also involved in providing maintenance support and conducting engineering services for B客户提供支持。</data>
  <data key="d9">collaboration,engineer-client relationship,engineering services,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance service,maintenance support,responsibility,service provision,support</data>
