<edge source="A人員" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">11.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(A人员, B客户) represents a relationship where A人员 provides various maintenance and support services to B客户. The primary responsibilities of A人员 include conducting maintenance activities on B客户的 systems and ensuring that these systems are functioning optimally. These tasks can involve both routine checks and more extensive engineering support as needed.

A人员 not only performs maintenance but also documents the work done, such as maintaining records related to system performance and issues encountered during service provision. For instance, A人员 has conducted a detailed maintenance record for B客户 involving Splunk software, illustrating the depth of technical involvement required in their role.

In some instances, A人员 may collaborate with other personnel, such as C人员, to ensure comprehensive coverage of all necessary maintenance activities for B客户的 systems and equipment. This collaborative effort ensures that multiple aspects of system health are addressed effectively, contributing to the overall reliability and longevity of B客户的 assets.

Throughout these descriptions, it is clear that A人员 plays a critical role in supporting B客户 by providing thorough maintenance services and maintaining detailed records of all relevant activities performed for their benefit.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員handled the maintenance record for B客戶on 2025/11/06 from 10:00 to 11:00.&lt;SEP&gt;A人员为B客户提供了维护服务，处理了相关工程问题。&lt;SEP&gt;A人員provided maintenance support and performed engineering tasks for B客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">engineering services,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance record,maintenance service,maintenance support,responsibility,service provision,support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede</data>
